{"word":"H8254 - שָׁקַל - shâqal - shaw-kal' - Pay","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁקַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâqal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-kal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Pay"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எண்ணிக்கொடு, கொடு, செலவழி, எண்ணு நிறு, நிறுத்து, நிறுக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to weigh, to weigh out, to pay out"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to weigh"},{"paragraph":"2) to weigh out (a price)"},{"paragraph":"3) used of grief (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be weighed"},{"paragraph":"2) to be weighed out"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>suspend</i> or <i>poise</i> (especially in trade): - pay, receive (-r), spend, X throughly, weigh."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4946 - מִשְׁקֹול - mishqôwl - mish-kole'/4946\">H4946</a>, <a href=\"#/H4948 - מִשְׁקָל - mishqâl - mish-kawl'/4948\">H4948</a>, <a href=\"#/H4949 - מִשְׁקֶלֶת - mishqeleth - mish-keh'-leth/4949\">H4949</a>, <a href=\"#/H8254 - שָׁקַל - shâqal - shaw-kal'/8254\">H8254</a>, <a href=\"#/H8255 - שֶׁקֶל - sheqel - sheh'-kel/8255\">H8255</a>, <a href=\"#/H8256 - שִׁקְמָה - shiqmâh - shik-maw'/8256\">H8256</a>"}]}